column2: create table weblog ( --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- --/H normalized web log entry -- describes a web hit ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- --/T See also the WebLogAll view that denomalizes the table. ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 		hitID		bigint identity(#,#) not null primary key,--/D unique identifier 		yy			smallint  not null,--/D year 		mm			tinyint  not null, --/D month 		dd			tinyint  not null, --/D day (UTC) 		hh			tinyint  not null, --/D hour (UTC) 		mi			tinyint  not null, --/D minute 		ss			tinyint  not null, --/D second 		theTime	    dateTime not null, --/D timestamp 		logID		smallint not null, --/D id of server that generated record /R LogSource 		clientIpID	int		 not null, --/D id of IP address that generated record /R IpMap   		opID		tinyint  not null, --/D id of Web Operation: GET, POST,... /R webOp   		stemID	    int		 not null, --/D id of web command stem e.g. getJpeg.asp? /R WebCommandStem 		paramsID    int      not null, --/D id of web command string e.g. ID=# /R WebCommandParams  		error		smallint not null, --/D HTTP status code 		agentStringID int	 not null, --/D webAgentString (e.g. Firefox) /R WebAgentString 		refererID	int		 not null, --/D page that pointed to this page /R WebReferer 		bytesOut	bigint	 not null, --/D Bytes in request 		bytesIn		int		 not null, --/D Bytes in reply 		elapsed		int		 not null, --/D elapsed time in ms (seems to be unreliable) 		isvisible	bit      not null, --/D flag says record is public
